    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Established diagnosis of acute upper gastrointestinal bleeding, confirmed by presence
             of hematemesis/ coffee ground vomiting, melena, as well as other clinical or
             laboratory evidence of acute blood loss from the upper gastrointestinal tract

          -  Written informed consent provided prior the start of participation in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who are unwilling or unable to provide informed consent.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
